#. socialStories.doctor.1
msgctxt "socialStories.doctor.1"
msgid "Today I am going to the doctor."
msgstr "Idag ska jag gå till doktorn."

#. socialStories.doctor.2
msgctxt "socialStories.doctor.2"
msgid "We arrive at the clinic."
msgstr "Vi kommer till mottagningen."

#. socialStories.doctor.3
msgctxt "socialStories.doctor.3"
msgid "I wait in the waiting room. I can read a book."
msgstr "Jag väntar i väntrummet. Jag kan läsa en bok."

#. socialStories.doctor.4
msgctxt "socialStories.doctor.4"
msgid "The doctor is nice. They check that I am healthy."
msgstr "Doktorn är snäll. De kollar att jag mår bra."

#. socialStories.doctor.5
msgctxt "socialStories.doctor.5"
msgid "All done! I did great!"
msgstr "Klart! Jag var jätteduktig!"

#. socialStories.friend.1
msgctxt "socialStories.friend.1"
msgid "My friend is coming to play!"
msgstr "Min kompis ska komma och leka!"

#. socialStories.friend.2
msgctxt "socialStories.friend.2"
msgid "The doorbell rings."
msgstr "Det ringer på dörren."

#. socialStories.friend.3
msgctxt "socialStories.friend.3"
msgid "I say hello and we decide what to play."
msgstr "Jag säger hej och vi bestämmer vad vi ska leka."

#. socialStories.friend.4
msgctxt "socialStories.friend.4"
msgid "We take turns and share. That is kind."
msgstr "Vi turas om och delar med oss. Det är snällt."

#. socialStories.friend.5
msgctxt "socialStories.friend.5"
msgid "We say goodbye. It was fun!"
msgstr "Vi säger hejdå. Det var kul!"

#. socialStories.haircut.1
msgctxt "socialStories.haircut.1"
msgid "Today I am getting a haircut."
msgstr "Idag ska jag klippa mig."

#. socialStories.haircut.2
msgctxt "socialStories.haircut.2"
msgid "I sit in the chair. It is like a throne!"
msgstr "Jag sitter i stolen. Den är som en tron!"

#. socialStories.haircut.3
msgctxt "socialStories.haircut.3"
msgid "The hairdresser cuts a little bit. It does not hurt."
msgstr "Frisören klipper lite. Det gör inte ont."

#. socialStories.haircut.4
msgctxt "socialStories.haircut.4"
msgid "I look great! I did it!"
msgstr "Jag ser bra ut! Jag klarade det!"

#. socialStories.name.doctor
msgctxt "socialStories.name.doctor"
msgid "Going to the Doctor"
msgstr "Gå till doktorn"

#. socialStories.name.friend
msgctxt "socialStories.name.friend"
msgid "Playing with a Friend"
msgstr "Leka med en kompis"

#. socialStories.name.haircut
msgctxt "socialStories.name.haircut"
msgid "Getting a Haircut"
msgstr "Klippa sig"

#. socialStories.name.school
msgctxt "socialStories.name.school"
msgid "A Day at School"
msgstr "En dag i skolan"

#. socialStories.name.store
msgctxt "socialStories.name.store"
msgid "Going to the Store"
msgstr "Handla i affären"

#. socialStories.school.1
msgctxt "socialStories.school.1"
msgid "It is morning. Time to get ready for school."
msgstr "Det är morgon. Dags att göra sig redo för skolan."

#. socialStories.school.2
msgctxt "socialStories.school.2"
msgid "I pack my bag with everything I need."
msgstr "Jag packar min väska med allt jag behöver."

#. socialStories.school.3
msgctxt "socialStories.school.3"
msgid "I say hello to my teacher and friends."
msgstr "Jag säger hej till min fröken och mina kompisar."

#. socialStories.school.4
msgctxt "socialStories.school.4"
msgid "We learn new things in class. It is fun."
msgstr "Vi lär oss nya saker. Det är kul."

#. socialStories.school.5
msgctxt "socialStories.school.5"
msgid "At lunchtime, I eat my food and play."
msgstr "Vid lunch äter jag min mat och leker."

#. socialStories.school.6
msgctxt "socialStories.school.6"
msgid "School is over. I go home. It was a good day!"
msgstr "Skolan är slut. Jag åker hem. Det var en bra dag!"

#. socialStories.store.1
msgctxt "socialStories.store.1"
msgid "We make a shopping list."
msgstr "Vi gör en inköpslista."

#. socialStories.store.2
msgctxt "socialStories.store.2"
msgid "We drive to the store."
msgstr "Vi åker till affären."

#. socialStories.store.3
msgctxt "socialStories.store.3"
msgid "I help find things and put them in the cart."
msgstr "Jag hjälper till att hitta saker och lägga dem i vagnen."

#. socialStories.store.4
msgctxt "socialStories.store.4"
msgid "We pay at the register."
msgstr "Vi betalar i kassan."

#. socialStories.store.5
msgctxt "socialStories.store.5"
msgid "We go home with our bags. Good job!"
msgstr "Vi åker hem med våra kassar. Bra jobbat!"

#. socialStories.title
msgctxt "socialStories.title"
msgid "Social Stories"
msgstr "Sociala berättelser"

